    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“上帝不复存在——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >撒旦高踞宝座。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要还有一位上帝勇士尚存一息，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那么救赎的曙光犹存。”<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/1922a493112e7ebf68d9642e9e67ee48.poster.avif?t=1759220092\" width=800 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/1922a493112e7ebf68d9642e9e67ee48.webm?t=1759220092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/1922a493112e7ebf68d9642e9e67ee48.mp4?t=1759220092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使命呼唤</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是最后的神父，必须深入地狱最深处，摧毁邪恶的根源。前路险恶，陷阱重重，熔岩与恐惧如影随形。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/719dbc32c375ff7a8efb96c80909e872.poster.avif?t=1759220092\" width=800 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/719dbc32c375ff7a8efb96c80909e872.webm?t=1759220092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/719dbc32c375ff7a8efb96c80909e872.mp4?t=1759220092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快意恩仇或谨慎前行——风格由你掌控。在探寻魔王居所的古老传说、收集地狱圣物的同时，磨练你的平台跳跃技艺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/4f0eedbae6a5b9f6e71da7c3192e1d96.poster.avif?t=1759220092\" width=800 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/4f0eedbae6a5b9f6e71da7c3192e1d96.webm?t=1759220092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/4f0eedbae6a5b9f6e71da7c3192e1d96.mp4?t=1759220092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>技能进阶</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消耗祝福点数提升移动能力。通关关卡与收集完整圣物皆可获得祝福点数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/a7c23ad4b66dba14ee5753ce22a01c59.poster.avif?t=1759220092\" width=796 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/a7c23ad4b66dba14ee5753ce22a01c59.webm?t=1759220092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/a7c23ad4b66dba14ee5753ce22a01c59.mp4?t=1759220092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>竞技排行</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与好友及全球玩家一较高下，争夺最速通关记录。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras/7243e3e365713dad6aa64072ec45291f.avif?t=1759220092\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379230/extras_big/7243e3e365713dad6aa64072ec45291f.avif?t=1759220092 width=800 height=286 /></span><strong><br>游戏亮点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >十重关卡——从幽暗蘑菇洞穴到冷峻野兽派巨构</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首轮体验约需1.5小时</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恐怖渗透的宗教氛围</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解构主义、野兽派与炼狱风格的建筑美学</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复古怀旧与现代元素交融的视觉盛宴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原创配乐——教堂圣咏、祭祀鼓点与工业噪音的惊艳融合</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔王的悬疑心理独白</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移动技能成长系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全球排行榜——与玩家竞速闯关</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜集神秘地狱圣物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驰骋巨型藤根</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驭远古巨蛇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
